<br>
My smithing was about 50 at the time I made the knife, but I have heard people with skills as low as 33 being successful.  To begin, combine 2 (unstacked) pieces of ore and one flask of water in a forge to make metal bits.  Metal bits triv at 22.  Next, make a scaler by combining one metal bits, one scaler mold, and one flask of water.  The scaler is triv at 41.  Finally you can make files by combining one metal bits with a skewer mold.  Files triv between 70 and 80.  That will be more than enuff to complete your quest <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
